
#
# This is a playbook for the Library.yaml file.  It is intended to be used
# with the sync_library role.  See the Library.yaml file for more information.
#
# The Library is populated from a sync source, which is defined in the
# Library.yaml file.  The sync source defines a set of content that should be
# included in the Library.  The sync source also defines a set of filters that
# can be used to control which content is included in the Library.  If a filter
# does not match, then the content is not included in the Library.  If no
# filters match, then all content is included in the Library.  Filters are applied
# in order and once a filter matches, subsequent filters are not evaluated.  If you
# want to include all content except for one type, then you should use an exclude
# filter instead of
